|               |                 Projection: supplier.s_nationkey, lineitem.l_extendedprice, lineitem.l_discount, lineitem.l_shipdate, customer.c_nationkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
